{
  "stem": "23090.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they told them that they'll be the last ones to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which was always, I guess, the best thing, is always to be the last to go, since where you were going, the rumors were that it wasn't a good place to go.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in that respect, it was a mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a good thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were hidden.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- There was a time where there-- the-- we didn't-- we wanted to stay as long as we could.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our doctor, which my dad later married, hid me and my sister in a-- in a attic for I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe a few days, a week, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because these things, when they were evacuating, they were taking them by blocks, by sections of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So once a section was supposedly evacuated, they had the police come in there-- the Jewish police, the people that-- that-- that would run the internal government-- go from apartment to apartment to make sure that everybody was gone.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of that search would require going through attics, basements, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, people are very innovative and very-- so they would just find ways of not reporting.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The system did not, I don't recall, and I'm not going to say that I knew, but I don't know that there was a roll call, you know, in terms of is a-- is Mr.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Smith there, is Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Jones there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was just that you went by blocks, and then the search began.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
